00:00:07.364 --> 00:00:09.784
today we will make sweet corn curry recipe.

00:00:10.057 --> 00:00:15.779
let's see what all ingredients are required for making sweet corn matar curry recipe.

00:00:16.938 --> 00:00:22.486
sweet corn - 2 (remove leaves and wash)

00:00:23.572 --> 00:00:26.874
green peas (frozen)
you can also use fresh peas.

00:00:27.559 --> 00:00:35.984
paste - 3-4 tomatoes,2 green chilly and 1 inch ginger piece

00:00:36.784 --> 00:00:39.840
coriander - 2-3 tbsp (finely chopped)

00:00:40.193 --> 00:00:43.193
garam masala - less then 1/4 tsp

00:00:43.584 --> 00:00:45.989
salt - .45 tsp or as per taste

00:00:46.349 --> 00:00:48.127
oil - 2-3 tbsp

00:00:48.606 --> 00:00:50.145
cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:50.512 --> 00:00:51.544
aafoetida - 1-2 pinch

00:00:52.102 --> 00:00:54.403
turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp

00:00:54.597 --> 00:00:56.517
coriander powder - 1 tsp

00:00:56.901 --> 00:00:59.067
red chilly powder - 1/4 tsp

00:00:59.728 --> 00:01:05.204
for making sweet corn curry we will first prepare corn curry.

00:01:06.330 --> 00:01:13.790
for making cream of sweet corn either rub knife over it  or grate it.

00:01:16.896 --> 00:01:18.634
we will grate it.

00:01:33.584 --> 00:01:38.385
now preheat pan and first roast peas.

00:01:39.591 --> 00:01:45.615
add 1 tbsp oil in preheated pan.

00:01:52.959 --> 00:01:57.690
add peas and saute for 3-4 minutes until they get crispy.

00:02:02.471 --> 00:02:05.955
by sauting frozen peas their taste is enhanced.

00:02:12.260 --> 00:02:16.118
peas are roasted now take them off from flame.

00:02:30.248 --> 00:02:41.765
take 1.5 tsp oil more and add cumin seeds into it.

00:02:48.739 --> 00:03:04.528
after suating cumins seeds add turmeric powder,coriander powder and tomto-chilly-ginger paste.

00:03:15.983 --> 00:03:23.217
also add red chilly powder and saute masala until oil starts floating on the surface.

00:03:32.932 --> 00:03:37.408
it will take 4-5 minutes in sauting masala.

00:03:38.278 --> 00:03:40.508
keep stirring masala after regular intervals.

00:03:51.117 --> 00:03:55.855
masala is ready now add cream into it.

00:04:02.343 --> 00:04:06.605
saute sweet corn cream with masala for 3-4 more minutes.

00:04:24.544 --> 00:04:35.636
now add 1 cup water or per your preference

00:04:38.958 --> 00:04:43.585
add more water as per requirement.

00:05:01.469 --> 00:05:02.532
add salt.

00:05:09.239 --> 00:05:13.167
the consistency of gravy can be kept thick or thin as per your choice.

00:05:13.584 --> 00:05:15.283
add some more water.

00:05:21.553 --> 00:05:39.159
also add peas,garam masala and mix all infredients nicely.

00:05:39.708 --> 00:05:47.838
cover and cook sabzi for 2-3 minutes so that all spices get absorbed in peas.

00:05:52.039 --> 00:05:54.515
open and stir sabzi.

00:06:02.114 --> 00:06:04.876
add green coriander in the end.

00:06:08.847 --> 00:06:11.169
sweet corn matar curry is ready.

00:06:11.417 --> 00:06:18.009
serve sweet corn matar curry with chapatti,makka roti,bajra roti or naan.

